WEBVTT

00:00.894 --> 00:01.897
<i>Hi I'm Chuck.</i>

00:01.922 --> 00:03.465
<i>Here are a few things that</i>
<i>you might need to know.</i>

00:03.606 --> 00:05.006
You really think
you've been fighting evil...

00:06.509 --> 00:07.742
<i>...doing good?</i>

00:08.677 --> 00:11.278
<i>You think it was all</i>
<i>a coincidence?</i>

00:11.312 --> 00:15.416
<i>The Intersect, FULCRUM,</i>
<i>the Ring, Shaw, Agent X?</i>

00:15.450 --> 00:18.485
<i>You're just a pawn,</i>
<i>you always were.</i>

00:18.520 --> 00:20.821
No, no, n-n-n-no,
don't take the Intersect.

00:20.839 --> 00:22.990
- You're fired, Chuck.
- No!

00:24.692 --> 00:26.359
Operation Bartowski is done.

00:26.394 --> 00:29.195
What if we went
into business for ourselves?

00:29.213 --> 00:32.531
Hartley turned over
all of Volkoff's assets to us.

00:32.549 --> 00:33.967
Our first purchase
was the Buy More

00:34.001 --> 00:35.402
and everything below it.

00:35.436 --> 00:36.670
Freelance spies.

00:36.704 --> 00:37.904
Under the radar, above the law.

00:37.939 --> 00:41.258
Oh, man, this is gonna be
so much fun.

00:41.309 --> 00:42.676
Nice.

00:48.583 --> 00:51.618
Guys... I know kung fu.

